.about_us
	.row
		.medium-12.columns
			%h1.about
				We've been in your shoes. 
.row
	.medium-12.columns
		%h5.summary
			%b pinpeg 
			helps students connect with top companies and recruiters - 
			%i response guaranteed. 
			Our platform allows students to connect with past interns and evaluate data on the internship experience. This collaborative effort will help students select and better prepare for their internships, as well as provide companies feedback about their internship programs and top talent. 
		%h1.aboutHead Our Story
		%h5.summary
			Karine and Lisa met during our sophomore summer internships at a VC firm. During the summer, we reflected on why and how we ultimately chose the internship we were at and discovered that both of us had gone into the summer with no idea of how it would actually turn out. Even though there had been several interns in the past, we hadn't known who to reach out to. So 
			%b pinpeg
			was started - to help students select internships and better prepare for the summer.
